com.vijfhart.casus.tree.tree

Class NodeTree<E extends Node<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vijfhart.casus.tree.tree.NodeTree<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeIterable<E>, Tree<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class NodeTree<E extends Node<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tree<E>
    An implementation of a tree. Nodes are stored in internal list, which will be sorted using a NodeTreeComparator when requesting an iterator.
    Author:
    Dirk Luijk
